snippet.title: Amazon Basic Monitor Arm Review - Great, But Keep This in Mind...
snippet.description:
Amazon Basic Monitor Arm: https://amzn.to/2TrimtF

If you're thinking of getting a monitor arm, this Amazon Basic Monitor Arm is a great choice but remember that the joints can limit some motion and could damage your cables. If you do decide to get this one, remember to leave enough slack for your cables!

I'm just starting out on YouTube, so every like and comment goes a long way! I appreciate all feedback, questions or criticisms! I'll be sure to answer all your questions to the best of my ability!

If you want to participate in giveaways (which you have a good shot at winning, as I have 4 subscribers), make sure to subscribe!
